，缩写：<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/MBA' target='_blank'>MBA</a>）*(2)</li>	<li>高级工商管理硕士（MBA for Executives，缩写：EMBA）*(3)</li>	<li>国际高级工商管理硕士（Global MBA for Executives，缩写：GEMBA）*(4)</li>	<li>工商管理博士（PhD in Business Administration）*(5)</li></ul><p>双学位项目：</p><ul>	<li>工商管理硕士/法学博士（MBA/<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/JD' target='_blank'>JD</a>）</li>	<li>工商管理硕士/医学博士（MBA/<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/MD' target='_blank'>MD</a>）</li>	<li>工商管理硕士/公共政策硕士（MBA/MPP）</li>	<li>工商管理硕士/公共卫生硕士（MBA/MPH）</li>	<li>工商管理硕士/教育学硕士（MBA/M.Ed）</li>	<li>工商管理硕士/工程硕士（MBA/ME）</li>	<li>工商管理硕士/护理硕士（MBA/MSN）</li>	<li>工商管理硕士/政府或外交硕士（MBA/MA in Government or Foreign Affairs）</li>	<li>工商管理硕士/东亚研究硕士（MBA/MA in East Asian Studies）</li>	<li>工商管理硕士/工商管理博士（MBA/PhD）*(6)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>教员列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=yrZqibewLMS38l3Df_cTzzar1nutsxRhoGSXBH1irqNYloYuuS25t7677FhYd2YgpUKStiiK67SutOZ9r6wxCtNwlw-bxha9Ac2qBDPrOC5E9N5AhVlaBQa' target='_blank'>Faculty Directory</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=BraKR4e8kyji7rYm2MU807YqPVHnCS-3u75ym7H-RXnR6iZvqCvACakni73yOiNafw_U1AdsAq42U6TJTplEfmPRWAJIOZPqKyTLYz9mioWIFMI__Exj-u9ioCRYzZh02' target='_blank'>Darden History</a> Darden School of Business, University of Virginia</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=crr9MjouwN_n-gGn-----K0XIFiruZ2dOBH8H8HIu3C8fyTvY3UeY6Cbp8VfK67fpSC5p6CrQB7QT3wD' target='_blank'>MBA</a> Darden School of Business, University of Virginia</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=XrChP9xKLLRfq8_ZttttttEBO8K93ej2udpdpdfbMAYktVQ91tlaftUoN0q4VkUGV03oT0jDx3pongUi8wX' target='_blank'>MBA for Executives</a> Darden School of Business, University of Virginia</p><p>(4) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=WrSJLFT8wiWP52QmLLLLLLKv2yYfZVQ4DtDtDnY8xtJUP1d8F7dg_OwBWn0fVd0BsO6BVOcy-dW0POYS-q' target='_blank'>Global MBA for Executives</a> Darden School of Business, University of V