​<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/会计' target='_blank'>会计</a>硕士（M.S. in <a href='http://www.qianmu.org/会计' target='_blank'>Accounting</a>），起薪：$59,056</li>	<li>​贸易硕士（M.S. in Commerce），起薪：$67,739*(1)</li></ul><p>贸易学院研究生阶段开设有以下学位项目，分别是：</p><ul>	<li>贸易硕士（M.S. in Commerce）</li>	<li>会计硕士（M.S. in Accounting）</li>	<li>信息技术管理硕士（M.S. in <a href='http://www.qianmu.org/管理学' target='_blank'>Management</a> of IT）*(2)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=DroIGDyyk8-j0xb9LLLLLksVPdwKsXYbcDcDQj2fOmFrZG2rqjOVdSViw_g6oygtqNBEo_VEfS2EBpriqSvEbGrzfNvZoS2ZoyJNcp7bMPWJtg29Q7s-' target='_blank'>Facts at a Glance-McIntire School of Commerce</a> University of Virginia</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=OrMxo-G6wKwjsY_N999999eskcLmoIr-bWbWfRXPdyxVHYXV6V0QmIOJmg0aEV0SivWuJ_Rb6NBG8NR5EjB54aFdeO-MX' target='_blank'>Programs-McIntire School of Commerce</a> University of Virginia</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3>贸易硕士</h3><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:16.9%">			<p><a href='http://www.qianmu.org/USNEWS排名' target='_blank'>USNEWS排名</a></p>			</td>			<td style="width:13.86%">			<p>-</p>			</td>			<td style="width:17.1%">			<p>学费</p>			</td>			<td style="width:13.38%">			<p>$53,538</p>			</td>			<td style="width:22.36%">			<p>申请截止日期</p>			</td>			<td style="width:16.38%">			<p>1月1日</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:16.9%">			<p><a href='http://www.qianmu.org/TOEFL' target='_blank'>TOEFL</a>要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:13.86%">			<p>100</p>			</td>			<td style="width:17.1%">			<p><a href='http://www.qianmu.org/GPA' target='_blank'>GPA</a>要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:13.38%">			<p>平均：3.2-3.8</p>			</td>			<td style="width:22.36%">			<p>可申请学期</p>			</td>			<td style="width:16.38%">			<p>秋季</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:16.9%">			<p><a href='http://www.qianmu.org/IELTS' target='_blank'>IELTS</a>要求</p>			</td>			<td style="w