奖学金：Fellowship、<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/TA' target='_blank'>TA</a>和<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/RA' target='_blank'>RA</a>，奖学金优先考虑授予PhD学生，M.Eng项目无奖学金。*(7)</p><p><strong>研究领域</strong></p><p>化学工程系有以下研究领域，分别是：</p><ul>	<li>生物技术与生物分子工程（Biotechnology &amp; Biomolecular Engineering）</li>	<li>能源与环境（Energy and the Environment）</li>	<li><a href='http://www.qianmu.org/材料科学与工程' target='_blank'>材料工程</a>与<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/纳米技术' target='_blank'>纳米技术</a>（Marerials Engineering &amp; <a href='http://www.qianmu.org/纳米技术' target='_blank'>Nanotechnology</a>）</li>	<li>模拟与复杂系统（Simulation &amp; Complex Systems）* (8)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>化学工程系宣传册：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=yrZqibDpkHN_VwlCD2q992_fIo4vv-nCYWIM0cm9YXjloF-idRSzzLYIhxC2slAsaT_mYwyMb6NqCnsf09fsTUqZUgHJBnRSpa2XxCaPDdvVdBfTRFwNiKuy6RS6FhGx3' target='_blank'>Department of Chemical Engineering Brochure</a>(PDF)</li>	<li>化学工程系研究生手册：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=0rRNYshNwu23CfUW1NNsBjFe1xVSBWX1FXOWgl0kdItUk2AUwd94n_26djFS8MMymzdfJJZnppcFFyN5xxqXDBbtWMtmQzBlYJlJldBh5RF7HkL4BqSWIhFs7zXTT2127ffJ23IJpf2hGib_sNd_OY0Xk' target='_blank'>Department of Chemical Engineering Graduate Programs Handbook</a>(PDF)</li>	<li>教员列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=yrZqibvXwF1EgzGn------gIKteC3p_jmaWnWnHg7MCfhUrMjLkokxneS2nKKt1BYs3UHziybIHt5dAjU71GYJSxL' target='_blank'>Faculty</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=brEVbye0wI0Gi4V1UUUUUU4N9cXoHl0-5o6f6fSTNBFAe_CGugXvS9yb2Wy5UujhoyfS3iqoZi0onqV_' target='_blank'>Graduate Studies in ChE</a> University of Virginia</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=1rdft_26wKwjsQPzUZ1go11iBNmVJBOB4OKUb6kWhbp7U9jm6B4XazLpcQFQ0eVhD0HdTmnsbJ7AhD4vx5qnCBpvs-bqdMhgo6rTmmN1bja2sXTI' target='_blank'>Graduate Student Degree Requirements</a> Department of Chemical Engineering, University of Virginia</p><p>(3) <a href='https://engineering.virginia.edu/departments/chemical-engineering/graduate-studies-che/?requirements.html#accordion62910' target='_blank'>GRADUATE ADMISSIONS</a> School of Engineering and Applied Science, University of Virginia</p><p>(4)<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=ErbpefU1wcXfY2cKeeeeeFU-weEp678NZ7vNw5AYbeO-nKqLi1pGucWDk4ygo6mjqdm-2PQx39Td5c1U-S1KpZgoSlXqOWUpaWLSsXgqY_O3IW4IA8Qm4Jlz7DLgUkSOS' target='_blank'> </a><a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=IrnDV7goLzABIrxT7ezfp4hruR9TxZ5-YrsX6hZG-OhFQ6in5r8GaNZssfqIbssF4gJSBlqf9S7xtrUigOCnu-OBnZ' target='_blank'>Estimated Graduate Cost of Attendance, 2019-20</a><a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=erlnE6y7LlbvUu4j3hmDn3Sm61lgn7Lt1ajorNkQhtP1GBnOdqEIlj8MhF-Dl2X1B3E-2A256vuuhyJTeBnOUa8XgXa4Dk-2IlM6jyotLjG1yZfia3tEwTs0cwo_jots_OhVeR-iM' target='_blank'>20</a>&nbsp;University of Virginia</p><p>(5) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=arBPkM5SwHR2VNgRllllllaoSnU1vrVJaEaEBmbQ6WbJfQj1yEA3C0HIh0uoVvjIfDf3lZHYfUjLds4OfBuIfB_3C0uqhL4mlT' target='_blank'>GRADUATE APPLICATION DEADLINES</a> School of Engineering and Applied Science, University of Virginia</p><p>(6) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Nr20uKNjL5VUFG98444444nHaHR0cDovMz6w6wvM1F74Wo5h7wk1NbkBNw60xB4-rZS' target='_blank'>Commonwealth Graduate Enginering Program</a> University of Virginia</p><p>(7) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=zrQ-nHVUws9rfxU2VVVVVVa4_kcLmoIr-bWbWfReVO2e-1V_mnW_Pn0S-n6zrKVkZivia-QSqi4kUmDU3MKaeO1UqMpU2vPFMf' target='_blank'>FINANCIAL AID</a> School of Engineering and Applied Science, University of Virginia</p><p>(8) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=WrSJLFKKkgdlWQE3Rk8cNGY5VisWORF_GIwOf4zdmauofUmXQ_G5Rhz8_PRW4nvQVfYCL8JR1fpHUEl4NANPhRcD' target='_blank'>Research in ChE</a> University of Virginia</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3>土木工程</h3><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" c