Systems Bioengineering）</li>	<li>组织工程与生物材料（Tissue Engineering &amp; Biomaterials）</li>	<li>肌肉骨骼生物工程（Musculoskeletal Bioengineering）*(6)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>生物医学工程系宣传册：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=trmo1nTvke4w3txsOMyGQ53AeZKNEzEUA3A86MzaYVQNyh1n3mg9NRo1zKRSM8Kq6hrUrQ0-4dLOYBiLkhpDYC_dHUg8HTU2-WC6LMxmS0jopuP8PP9KXISIDPvGAOzfV' target='_blank'>Department of Biomedical Engineering Brochure</a>(PDF)</li>	<li>研究生项目手册：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=rrcuJRvIkJVBTZ_7mmmmmmFMOX-yrwsecHp6fS52a9JUHK5xkOVxEGWF2G0foTsM2O5ILYRqqTsINTRf4JLuhQ16zX0Is' target='_blank'>Department of Biomedical Engineering Graduate Program Handbook</a>(PDF)</li>	<li>研究生课程列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=3rHk7mgVwAbLSeHq666666O3TC9NPaDMhLOIH8h3_LR3CiXCGgdm-QS4VQaw2QSK2Eg4VqO0u1fc-1BmrEguI' target='_blank'>Course Descriptions</a></li>	<li>教员列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=3rHk7mgqweEscWzDmmmmmmMhUvfrF2WuqzRNJ1jf9RZh9Bj8V1jDJcr-H4Y-H4bDIfDdcLU-rsjRaEyZ' target='_blank'>Faculty</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Nr20uKHNwu23Cta3CCCCCCSH3TC9NPaDYKb_ICe2bQvF7Bvx1H1DNQeM7aAokGm9kxh9uN93625ZwAfseY5DMpXet' target='_blank'>Graduate Program</a> BME Department, University of Virginia</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Lr8sWSLDLZv0OWY0CCCCCC3TUajvqxFWIYZ-krITEYQTbr3Hkvlq_cvH_4-z_cbzJhvH_RUTrRzKEXx' target='_blank'>Frequently Asked Questions</a> BME Department, University of Virginia</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Erbpefw9Ln0yNcCHYYYYYYiMbIUERyVPQXQXOT75p97P65nEeXn3eotPe8dX-Bt5b5nEAoZ5OB6Wgs867kG53B4K8cOdsvG5SXUt2V' target='_blank'>APPLICATION INSTRUCTIONS</a> School of Engineering and Applied Science, University of Virginia</p><p>(4)<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=mrtw23qhk5gAr-k5BBBBJ-ZUcqNFolCjvEfxhrG51v3tSw-jhv19Gg-jDgo9Cru9hv3