<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/化学' target='_blank'>化学</a>：腐蚀、电沉积、能量转换（Electrochemistry: Corrosion, Electro-Deposition, Energy Conversion）</li>	<li>电子材料（Electronic Materials）</li>	<li>疲劳与断裂（Fatigue and Fracture）</li>	<li>耐高温材料（High Temperature Materials）</li>	<li>激光加工（Laser Processing）</li>	<li>磁性与自旋电子学（Magnetism and Spintronics）</li>	<li>冶金（Metallurgy）</li>	<li>相变（Phase Transformations）</li>	<li>表面科学与薄膜（Surface Science and Thin Films）*(6)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>材料科学与工程系宣传册：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=BraKR4scLYq_Z9jJ66666SS2L3YrbBXoG5G5sRKDxEKo7Dzr85zP890o8gZ5t40i84p5J4mr845QW_54CDpZtBLXFxi8C5rvtXrQW_54CMH1CB7' target='_blank'>Department of Materials Science &amp; Engineering Brochure</a>(PDF)</li>	<li>教员列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=wrYmhlZ-wDMZusAMw-bdpqBkG5FMoTUB-eDOnUmmhV8rlDZJWFfkKLCbOxhgvxZR0tZB0zcen8umB2mNWUzfDdH_PoeDstFfhSp7I' target='_blank'>Faculty</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=VrxbIdtSL1wLXKkFvvvvvvdfV-Ek6c1JApAtyV7wCvmL-umXlgS9HpgWmoaXQ9spQyqGGNjdrIYyhNyCh6' target='_blank'>Estimated Graduate Cost of Attendance, 2019-20</a><a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=ArAjQun5wfFe8h-dGGGGG0mweEp678N_JXgHsQ9ReKlDzXgR9OswzXxwo-OfHPOgRejNHsQlDmclDdOhweGuHsapYsg34BnkXtaZtLnTwOoBfcKeHk8O6M6' target='_blank'>20</a>&nbsp;University of Virginia</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Rr0CBrM7LlbvUhihNNNNNNQI03C14IO8gsFIFIrQXz9NpHMD9jmnHG5-H0mpA_O9BV7bjr8EZ5xEYfOzWmOMOI5Fxj47fLiWCcq6cRSgl_yv9KIt' target='_blank'>GRADUATE ADMISSIONS</a>&nbsp;School of Engineering and Applied Science, University of Virginia</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=XrChP9QkkniNS4EYVZQvtGYve9gWOC3Yo1mGEXKyP1aPzrIWxRbbPueVN-CVPW_wglx_JOwaUHy5CgZokoBd7_qGnkGncaU-K632D_-CqLTPwI' target='_blank'>Graduate Curriculum</a>&nbsp;School of Engineering and Applied Science, Universi