力系统与控制（Dynamical Systems And Control）：包括振动控制，转子动力学，磁轴承，机电一体化，流体控制、机器人与神经动力控制、周期控制系统及其性能提升等</li>	<li>热流体（Thermofluids）：包括微观与非傅里叶热传导、燃烧（含超音速）、降阶<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/化学' target='_blank'>化学</a>动力学、热声、气凝胶、远程化学试剂检测、远程生物制剂检测、低速非定常气动流、重返大气层流动、超音速混合、注入式液体离心分离机、流动式离心泵、叶轮机械流动、生物流体力学、流体动力学及其稳定性、微重力流体力学、多自由表面流动、非牛顿型流体机械、流体结构及其相互作用、自由与强制对流等* (7)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>机械与航空航天工程系宣传册：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=hrfXwivaLhsIeJihNNNNNxxXtru7-W_UaOaOpc3sD63UIsR7LORqLYSJ8hMU1HNJ9hNy1fN4RhNFK9dWI7iBYJNV1wKl_b2tZsN-ZpJztX2RAH2Vy' target='_blank'>Department of Mechanical and Areospace Engineering Brochure</a>(PDF)</li>	<li>研究生项目手册：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=jr4AsclFwX5FZjm2w03EtTOUIKRkXBRhaC4VxhfffyRQ3nCSGzIXKLwJhyfWKhu6XaLhZ14Oj1LhhdP8xtJhNdxa4DbmYVOPb61dNVrOyCgUzIMMfmIXxKUHQhMQdhyue4foRWh0_v5BN_PwkDfEFdUBNPR' target='_blank'>Department of Mechanical and Aerospace Engineering Graduate Student Handbook</a>(PDF)</li>	<li>研究生项目要求：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=mrtw23qyk8-j0BE2bRrWma_KL3pG_Fu3vyPqqsSk_XcUgqkwaU_i8EUIpk3RAvbH-eHCbfvz1MjFCQubFE6J7RKaNFE6NMma4NMb7oEPmxJNb95Q_O23GskSW_1QV_vKob3RAUTXZfk_X0G9S0zPRrqdHF17emE48sDI06Pmzprj3HKPwxT' target='_blank'>MAE Department Memorandum</a>(PDF)</li>	<li>教员列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=8rL6TCdxwGY_PU5pbbbbbbLARjDXMlLo6f6fSTeZuv2fHsSUys2Aui2UujhoDTsfDhdjnPeZuveUH1MbrZgXwoE' target='_blank'>MAE Faculty</a></li>	<li>教员研究组/实验室：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=kr53aGbIkJVBTZEtOOOOOO6rjEnLNxQShMkMk9s-qmA4kj89uV84Rmy4umB5hLs8kL5lBO6OipVOm9VBLhcKipVOm9VBLhcUNS0KUS_2C' target='_blank'>Faculty Research</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=ArAjQuFgkKhq9sBMIG2I_O3emEkaDWhUhKG5E77sY-SJ4teoBPM3p6FrGiUpywt3zFURHVtZe8GwCF5BWnIS73wk4U4I1M_AMG' target='_blank'>MAE Graduate MAE Department, </a>University of Virginia</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" h