 theory）</li>	<li>交换代数与代数几何（commutative algebra and algebraic geometry）</li>	<li>群论（group theory）</li>	<li>谐波分析测量法（harmonic analysis）</li>	<li>数学史（history of mathematics）</li>	<li>低维拓扑（low-dimensional topology）</li>	<li>数学<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/物理' target='_blank'>物理</a>（mathematical physics）</li>	<li>PDE理论（pde&#39;s）</li>	<li>概率论（probability）</li>	<li>算子理论（operator theory）</li>	<li>统计与分析（statistics and analysis）*(8)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>课程描述：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=BraKR4eCk3FezdS7v5S5IiYkyZDcynv3ARUodS5nmsJAUeR8VYhLqv-HicYA0pt-057_6tenhh5MCDjLXDR8EY2GLi03C' target='_blank'>Graduate Course Descriptions</a></li>	<li>教员及其研究列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=ArAjQunxwGY_PV5soO_bm0Bih95zKbXh7RPNJohMB5gy-n1qr1nAsIkg0GfswfLUJ3wF1mmmyG3DfW0blUAz2f4loeA8' target='_blank'>Faculty Research Areas</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=brEVbyf7LlbvUhihNNNNNN8URY1CdUmc8SvKi3rJLDZVFBjpFN-P9RAY9xox05yWNj-ZYHEai' target='_blank'>Graduate Program</a> Department of Mathematics, University of Virginia</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Rr0CBrsIkJVBTo_5gI_mCE_ktDm_YydCMylqyH43RF0HO1lhD_2YLUYG7GUwLfsyncPUrdfRciHoYHOXOGOiZ_hpUGYsFvUGkxLwkJePe3N7yTUICasldM9CSCCIgKa9VjYX4SOrdsw35bClw0H2R7hmGZjHb_8LY' target='_blank'>Mathematics Degree Requirements</a> Graduate Record, University of Virginia</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=trmo1nT-kSyncF8rgTo17G33nWVptzw_EYOSe2zBU-rNv17IMmjdnFQYCdPuKGl065RRFYExPV4NYbUYi-rdIR7PCldxnkC1I' target='_blank'>Admissions</a> Department of Mathematics, University of Virginia</p><p>(4) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=orDtO5cgwEi9XuU2VVVVVVC4R5Tsj9M0D1yWrNPFyXah-1aFxfBF-fTKBYEOJzUsQ0OPQ8UlVxNBbtYBTQUs59aiG' target='_blank'>Admission Requirements</a> Graduate School of Arts &amp; Sciences, University of Virginia</p><p>(5) <a rel="nofollo