ity of Virginia</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2>建筑学院</h2><p>弗吉尼亚大学<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/建筑学' target='_blank'>建筑学</a>院（School of Architecture）研究生阶段开设有以下学位项目，分别是：</p><ul>	<li>建筑史硕士（Master of Architectural <a href='http://www.qianmu.org/历史' target='_blank'>History</a>）</li>	<li>建筑学硕士（专业学位）（Master of Architecture, Professional Degree）</li>	<li><a href='http://www.qianmu.org/景观设计' target='_blank'>景观设计</a>硕士（Master of Landscape Architecture）</li>	<li>城市与环境规划硕士（Master of Urban and Environmental Planning）</li>	<li>建筑环境博士（PhD in the Constructed Environment）*(1)(2)(3)(4)(5)</li></ul><p>双学位项目：</p><p>弗吉尼亚大学建筑学院与其他学院共同开设的常见双学位项目有：</p><ul>	<li>建筑学-景观设计（Architecture &mdash; Landscape Architecture）</li>	<li>建筑史-建筑学（History of Architecture &mdash; Architecture）</li>	<li>景观设计-规划（Landscape Architecture &mdash; Planning）</li>	<li>建筑学-规划（Architecture &mdash; Planning）</li>	<li>规划-<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/法学' target='_blank'>法学</a>（Planning &mdash; <a href='http://www.qianmu.org/法学' target='_blank'>Law</a>）*(6)</li></ul><p><strong>录取统计</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:20.0%">			<p>招生年份</p>			</td>			<td style="width:20.0%">			<p>招生人数</p>			</td>			<td style="width:20.0%">			<p>女生比例</p>			</td>			<td style="width:20.0%">			<p>国际学生比例</p>			</td>			<td style="width:20.0%">			<p>TOEFL均分</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:20.0%">2016</td>			<td style="width:20.0%">122</td>			<td style="width:20.0%">			<p>-</p>			</td>			<td style="width:20.0%">-</td>			<td style="width:20.0%">-</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:20.0%">2015</td>			<td style="width:20.0%">			<p>63</p>			</td>			<td style="width:20.0%">54.0%</td>			<td style="width:20.0%">-</td>			<td style="width:20.0%">95.5</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:20.0%">			<p>2014</p>			</td>			<td style="width:20.0%">			<p>96</p>			</td>			<td style="width:20.0%">			<p>60%</p>			</td>			<td style="width:20.0%">			<p>15%</p>			</td>			<td style="width:20.0%">			<p>98</p