zogxyOaGBJn4CXbj7X_9UgMrQ-IEx' target='_blank'>Facts &amp; Statistics-School of Law</a> University of Virginia</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=QrzUA2uDLZv0OpM_Jw2d7vrjobKZkdGq8cA-Fn7DSzNvf4h9ArU08QlReQrdlzQ8XuKqFXAwbl57aEGBfN2cLaY6GLyYoNqlRSAbl4hh3VtHaCLXSaauPjVpGqiMM3vVR' target='_blank'>LL.M. and S.J.D. Application Instructions</a> University of Virginia</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3>JD项目</h3><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:16.24%">			<p><a href='http://www.qianmu.org/USNEWS排名' target='_blank'>USNEWS排名</a></p>			</td>			<td style="width:16.64%">			<p>8</p>			</td>			<td style="width:14.96%">			<p>学费</p>			</td>			<td style="width:14.98%">			<p>$60,528</p>			</td>			<td style="width:19.96%">			<p>申请截止日期</p>			</td>			<td style="width:17.22%">			<p>3月3日</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:16.24%">			<p><a href='http://www.qianmu.org/TOEFL' target='_blank'>TOEFL</a>要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:16.64%">			<p>Not Required</p>			</td>			<td style="width:14.96%">			<p><a href='http://www.qianmu.org/GPA' target='_blank'>GPA</a>要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:14.98%">			<p>平均：3.90</p>			</td>			<td style="width:19.96%">			<p>可申请学期</p>			</td>			<td style="width:17.22%">			<p>秋季</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:16.24%">			<p><a href='http://www.qianmu.org/IELTS' target='_blank'>IELTS</a>要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:16.64%">			<p>-</p>			</td>			<td style="width:14.96%">			<p><a href='http://www.qianmu.org/LSAT' target='_blank'>LSAT</a>要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:14.98%">			<p>平均：170</p>			</td>			<td style="width:19.96%">			<p>工作经验要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:17.22%">			<p>无</p>			</td>		</tr>	</tbody></table><p>*(1)(2)(3)</p><p>注：</p><p>（1）此处排名为<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/2020USNEWS%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E6%B3%95%E5%AD%A6%E9%99%A2%E6%8E%92%E5%90%8D' target='_blank'>2020USNEWS美国法学院排名</a></p><p>（2）此处学费针对的是2019-20学年。需要注意的是，该费用每年