得了奖学金，该金额一般也不超过学费的三分之一，不会将学费、生活费等通通囊括进去。该奖学金无需单独申请，只在录取并确认前往弗吉尼亚大学后方才发放。*(4)</p><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=MrO2caR6LFLdYNSWPLw2lJSfIaMobPywrz0SFxizabKsDKXhGS9cy8MOHGtwwLY50F1wkO0rbOgwtAq4aKNChq_Ij6MR6Jq7xMPCaMfw0OW6dd6L-S0gPjqoYaFZ-JKVR' target='_blank'>LL.M. and S.J.D. Application Instructions</a> University of Virginia</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=5rk_5oa-wDMZus1QbiTbZI1ywBL5nBPFXOe3fkdvdB34v0j1HfYliocumKFdA8Hvw5uhHmyrB2-qOowPvoOcAdZ3Qwm2yxfdIjrb64KBBCQF56kN1rheSBURxzd6ipa0BY' target='_blank'>Application Checklist-LLM</a> University of Virginia</p><p>(3)<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=PrgaXq8SL1wLXKgommmmmqEeK4sVpB03lDTjHtwL3c6vynYWd52wfhHjSpLYTbr3Hkri1hACsQbvwkb-IJbFPn87BVw8vMmuy74DsQF0p2_zgehgE23SwBjQWKycUwOvO' target='_blank'> </a><a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=ArAjQunywRjyJ_Dz77777rnpAb5PTjHRQ-Q-o3LpxnspU3O1l3NhAmH1sS9hPJdmnmsSupRSR9NCwt9dYkVQhOUMPQzdhkDqZBoqfLUehkDXGFDpSFDpEFUqvBb' target='_blank'>2019-2020&nbsp;Tuition &amp; Fees</a><a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=kr53aG4SL1wLXypaRRRRRfWZMtTeh6yAU2nID7i4M5EBs2n4iSDBOngrOSz-4LzNx8BmQuXYoGaJoG4OfvSgMuXA8-X0PqFwihHAenseou_yQvZwx6XbNvEv' target='_blank'> </a>University of Virginia</p><p>(4) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=KruBHNW7kjzL8RVi888888BZoVQmCuLxgFrKrKzdkhHIR85vxXUXjI_squ_hlFp-nqfCcd8VNfkmNZCzJgizQZ7jYmQ6WjZbT-_Yre7iOo0Q8XR' target='_blank'>Frequently Asked Questions-LLM</a> University of Virginia</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2>医学院</h2><p>弗吉尼亚大学<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/医学' target='_blank'>医学</a>院（School of MEdicine）开设的学位项目如下</p><ul>	<li>医学博士（<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/MD' target='_blank'>MD</a>）</li>	<li>普通学者项目（Generalist Scholars Program）：是针对住院<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/医师' target='_blank'>医师</a>的</li>	<li>医学博士与<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/哲学' target='_blank'>哲学</a>博士（MD-PhD）</li>	<li>医学博士-工商管理硕士（MD-<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/MBA' target='_blank'>MBA</a>）</li>	<li>医学博士-<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/公共卫生' target='_blank'>公共卫生</a>硕士（MD-MPH）</li>	<li>医学博士-临床研究医学科学（MD-CR：MD-Medical Science in Clinical Research）*(1)</li></ul><p><strong>申请条件</strong></p><p>弗吉尼亚大学医学院各项目要求学生至少在美国、加拿大或英国修过90个学分以上，方才有资格申请。90个学分一般需3年完成；</p><p>最好毕业于美国大学，并取得学士学位*(2)</p><p>注：上述这些条件也意味着国内的学生是无法直接申请的。</p><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=arBPkMoOLi1FD43R111Z77heplP6qL459yDyDSbYHmPefzECH0bzpRFKpmbef0bEHli5HmPxfzrtJ3og0mGPVUKVYloIH5zpPUKw0OiXsWrw8FBxK0CMpBZEOBhEeB6Ee9qEO2n3x2q5pInWA9cPp8dXpjtX_oV3xTyX_2c' target='_blank'>Programs in Medical Education</a> University of Virginia</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=orDtO5ZLks07EKDDIIIIIhOqYJqE2-iwe_OvOvBhCOpgTP9bmDOpnAbhVBNvWLYvUPYanutASumB5DEzZB0QsOfL21lZGljBMZsILAn_jjiAa7E1JNKlJkQHfeVbGR5YaR3xg2iMw-vld3SYEcykA0P5iNAOsG9O5hmXsBMJIpuwJpdu9THILYsq7slyB' target='_blank'>General Requirements-School of MEdicine</a> University of Virginia</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2>护理学院</h2><p>弗吉尼亚大学<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/护理' target='_blank'>护理</a>学院（School of Nursing）开设有以下四种学位项目：</p><ul>	<li>护士管理硕士项目（Master&#39;s Entry: Clinical Nurse Leader program）</li>	<li>护理硕士项目（&zwnj;Master of Science in Nursing，缩写MSN）</li>	<li>护理博士（PhD in Nursing）</li>	<li>临床护理博士（Doctor of Nursing Practice，缩写DNP）*(1)</li></ul><p><strong>申请条件</strong></p><p>国际学生必需拥有美国<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/注册护士' target='_blank'>注册护士</a>（RN）资格，方才可以申请，录取后还必需获得<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/弗吉尼亚州' target='_blank'>弗吉尼亚州</a>的注册护士（RN）资格。这一条件也意味着国内学生是无法直接申请的。*(2)</p><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=0rRNYshbw4VCAr0OKKKKKKc7btTxCNRj4I4Il6LI3kJ7v69j9mBxAIBwA_aamD2lJLNVFdI6sgb6pUPQmB' target='_blank'>Graduate Programs-School of Nursing</a> University of Virginia</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=erlnE6b8wiWP5BbMqnzGoJhF5poimPvBL8v4bwhmFwGa_rOKghalSA